Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.02,0:00:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial Black\pos(316,325)\fad(400,0)}Obey the Rules and manners\Nto have a fun Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.90,0:00:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Light so glaring that it can't be hidden shatters the silence and revives in this world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.91,0:00:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The violently quaking and thirsty Earth stakes its life and clashes together with sparks
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.67,0:00:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just one more time is enough to create a miracle
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.89,0:00:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For the power to regain the pages of memory lost in the past
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.81,0:00:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fs30}The believing heart that penetrates the darkness searches for the place where its soul sleeps
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.11,0:01:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And burns a sharp glance of eyes that can't sparkle
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.49,0:01:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Two hearts of light and shadow head toward the future that the crystal reflects
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.83,0:01:14.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now they start to move, these eyes brimming red
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.40,0:01:31.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kaiba-{\i0}kun{\i1} suddenly came into the Final Match of the KC Grand Prix.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.94,0:01:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With the fate of Kaiba Corporation at stake, he faced off against Sieg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.03,0:01:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He attacked over and over with the Goddess Combo he used to torture Jounouchi-{\i0}kun{\i1}...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.28,0:01:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But Kaiba-{\i0}kun{\i1}'s confidence never wavered.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.83,0:01:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And he defeated Sieg with a final winning attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.46,0:01:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, that is indeed something Kaiba-{\i0}kun{\i1} would do...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.54,0:01:57.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Final Battle for Duel King - \NYugi VS Leon"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.43,0:02:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm never pleased when Kaiba wins,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.18,0:02:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but we can't let that arrogant bastard do whatever he pleases.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.48,0:02:11.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, he was just doing this because of some grudge he had, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.81,0:02:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a troublesome guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.48,0:02:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he's also a very strong Duelist...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.24,0:02:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why must he resort to this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.07,0:02:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Other Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.70,0:02:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kaiba, you showed me your strong spirit as a Duelist in this Duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.67,0:02:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi, now the trouble-making rat is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.76,0:02:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now it's your turn to show me a Duel fitting the Duel King.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.01,0:02:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.76,0:02:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're really great, Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.06,0:02:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With that, I've shown rivaling companies all around the world
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.52,0:02:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,just how foolish it is to oppose Kaiba Corporation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.73,0:02:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning that wasn't just a waste of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.99,0:03:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.74,0:03:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isono.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.03,0:03:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.70,0:03:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up on the preparations for Yugi and Leon's Duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.37,0:03:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.29,0:03:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what should we do with that person?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.08,0:03:13.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let him be! He can't do anything now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.42,0:03:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.80,0:03:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll show him how successful Kaiba Corporation is!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.81,0:03:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now, I shall announce it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.64,0:03:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The KC Grand Prix held by the Kaiba Corporation...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.90,0:03:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An outstanding participant has emerged!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.02,0:03:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leon Wilson!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.03,0:03:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He will be granted the most honorable right as a Duelist!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.83,0:03:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That is, the right to challenge the Duel King, Yugi Mutou!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.33,0:03:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The most exciting match is about to start!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.52,0:04:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the stage for the final battle, Blue-Eyes Castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.69,0:04:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great! There are priority seats!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.56,0:04:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure this is fine, Mokuba-{\i1}kun{\i0}?\N To invite us to watch from here...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.74,0:04:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.70,0:04:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys helped me out a ton of times when I was in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.74,0:04:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The least I can do is give you the best seats to root for Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.16,0:04:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Mokuba-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.00,0:04:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The battle for the title of the true Duel King is about to start!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.29,0:04:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.88,0:04:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Other Me, it's finally here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.76,0:04:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.63,0:04:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The opponent is Leon-{\i1}kun{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.59,0:04:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure it will be an interesting Duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.35,0:04:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's do our best to have a Duel with no regrets!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.81,0:04:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.86,0:05:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Partner!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.85,0:05:38.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To the viewers all over the world, can you feel it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.31,0:05:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The excitement! The anticipation! And the cheers of the huge crowd here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.57,0:05:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here comes the Duel King, Yugi Mutou!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.04,0:06:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi-{\i1}san{\i0}, I finally made it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.92,0:06:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been my dream to have a Duel with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.22,0:06:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've gone through countless Duels to fulfill my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.85,0:06:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But today...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.81,0:06:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now the match of the century, the battle for the title of Duel King is about to start!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.94,0:06:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Who will emerge the winner? Will it be Leon Wilson?! Or Yugi Mutou?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.32,0:06:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have a great Duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.49,0:06:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leon...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.66,0:06:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now the two of them are ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.21,0:06:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And this person shall announce the start of the Duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.42,0:06:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm {\i0}gonna?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.05,0:06:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like hell you would! It'll be my big brother! My {\i1}big brother{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.39,0:06:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.47,0:07:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The KC Grand Prix is organized by Kaiba Corporation!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.23,0:07:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This program is also brought to you by Kaiba Corporation!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.15,0:07:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh man.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.23,0:07:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba's hogging the spotlight again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.11,0:07:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.40,0:07:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This Duel tournament is an important event that concerns the future of Kaiba Corporation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.49,0:07:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But rather than standing there, wouldn't Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0} want to battle with Yugi again?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.66,0:07:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... In fact, my big brother is the only one who is most qualified to Duel with Yugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.50,0:07:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Kaiba Corporation is what's most important right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.25,0:07:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather, he's standing there for our dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.34,0:07:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, as a Duelist, I understand his feelings of wanting to fight with Yugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.68,0:07:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to fight him as well, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.97,0:07:41.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Leon earned his right by having the skill to defeat all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.69,0:07:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, I hope he'll do his best on behalf of the Duelists who were defeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.28,0:07:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You stand before us, having survived intense battles with Duelists from all over the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.28,0:07:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is your greatest honor to be able to stand there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.99,0:07:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And within this battlefield,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.62,0:08:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you must show the world a battle worthy of the title for Duel King!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.67,0:08:06.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now, as you seek the greatest victory...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.92,0:08:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Duel starts now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.13,0:08:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I come!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.30,0:08:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll attack first!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.39,0:08:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.18,0:08:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Forest Wolf in Attack Position!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.64,0:08:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forest Wolf? What kind of card is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.81,0:08:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.86,0:08:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn end.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.36,0:08:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.78,0:08:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.28,0:08:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From my hand, I activate a Magic Card...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.62,0:08:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.70,0:08:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will fuse two Monsters I have in my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.79,0:08:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I fuse Illusion Beast Gazelle and Berfomet together!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.46,0:08:53.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To Summon Winged Phantom Beast Chimera!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.72,0:08:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I use Chimera to attack Forest Wolf!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.02,0:09:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Way to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.73,0:09:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great! Yugi's in the lead!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.94,0:09:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn over!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.40,0:09:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi-{\i1}san{\i0} is indeed strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.57,0:09:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By Dueling with you like this, I can really feel your oppressive aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.99,0:09:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have always dreamed about dueling with you like this, Yugi-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.16,0:09:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what form it may take, my dream has come true!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.00,0:09:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn, draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.71,0:09:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Little Red Riding Hood in Defense Position!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.17,0:09:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.97,0:09:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like Leon has many cards like that in his deck...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.18,0:09:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it feels like a deck full of childhood tales!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.22,0:09:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get deceived just because they look cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.85,0:09:47.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.56,0:09:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wouldn't know how strong he really is unless you've fought with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.82,0:09:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn end!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.86,0:09:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? He's not placing any reverse cards?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.90,0:09:57.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This really is strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.78,0:10:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's different from how I felt when he fought with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.03,0:10:02.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leon Wilson...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.62,0:10:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.79,0:10:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've gotten a feel of his Dueling style while monitoring the Duelists.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.04,0:10:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is something different about him now...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.17,0:10:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Or does it mean he wasn't serious before now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.13,0:10:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's going on with Leon-{\i0}kun{\i1}?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.43,0:10:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Partner...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.76,0:10:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He always looked like he enjoyed the Duels before...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.97,0:10:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But now...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.81,0:10:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, there's certainly something different about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.94,0:10:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Those are not of same eyes Leon had when he was enjoying his Duels.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.19,0:10:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.66,0:10:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.28,0:10:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is this possible?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.08,0:10:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I better go inform Seto-{\i1}sama{\i0} right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.44,0:11:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Retrained Elf Swordsman in Attack Position!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.03,0:11:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I use Retrained Elf Swordsman to attack Little Red Riding Hood!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.84,0:11:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great! Yugi had yet another successful attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.34,0:11:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel bad for Leon, but I think Yugi's gonna emerge as the winner!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.43,0:11:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not going to be so easy, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.47,0:11:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leon's deck is full of Monsters with Special Effects.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.68,0:11:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate Little Red Riding Hood's Special Ability!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.10,0:11:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When this card is destroyed in battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.65,0:11:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can Special Summon a Level Four or lower Warrior-Type Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.90,0:12:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Special Summon Forest Hunter in Attack Position!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.70,0:12:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And when Forest Hunter is Summoned successfully...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.20,0:12:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One Monster on the opponent's field will be removed from the game!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.75,0:12:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.59,0:12:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! Forest Hunter, get rid of Chimera!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.06,0:12:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.31,0:12:40.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, there are many Monsters with unknown powers in Leon's deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.07,0:12:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the Leon now is different from the Leon that I fought with.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.32,0:12:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.07,0:12:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's probably just nervous, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.66,0:12:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When he was Dueling with me, he seemed to really be enjoying the Duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.21,0:12:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But now that he's finally fighting with his idolized Yugi, he doesn't seem happy at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.29,0:13:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I end my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.84,0:13:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.97,0:13:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The True Duelist whom I've admired...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.68,0:13:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been my dream to fight with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.68,0:13:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But now, I'm fighting with you for the sake of my mission, Yugi-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.10,0:13:18.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mission?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.27,0:13:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad, Seto-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.32,0:13:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Please look at these!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.49,0:13:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To prevent further incidents, I continued checking the backgrounds of the Duelists.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.28,0:13:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And this is what I found!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.37,0:13:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph, so that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.66,0:13:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you finally get it, Kaiba.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.12,0:13:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sieg, is this your strategy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.87,0:13:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is right. Everything is going according to my plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.54,0:13:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think that another son of the Schroeder family
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.80,0:13:45.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,would enter this competition with a fake name.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.38,0:13:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.76,0:13:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. He is my authentic younger brother as well as a genuine Dueling genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.18,0:13:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leonhart von Schroeder!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.23,0:13:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Leonhart! Playtime is over!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.48,0:14:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show him your true abilities!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.23,0:14:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.28,0:14:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.40,0:14:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leon-{\i1}kun{\i0}, what's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.03,0:14:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Leon-{\i0}kun{\i1}...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.03,0:14:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would appear that you not only got cocky,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.53,0:14:14.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you let your guard down after defeating me, Kaiba.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.24,0:14:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I have already prepared my next move.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.54,0:14:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On this grand stage that Kaiba Corporation has painstakingly set up
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.75,0:14:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for the entire world to see...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.63,0:14:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Duel King, Yugi Mutou, will be utterly defeated by my Leonhart.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.80,0:14:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What would everyone think after witnessing that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.10,0:14:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naturally, the name "Schroeder" would be deeply etched in their hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.93,0:14:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And at that very moment, we Schroeders will announce our new game product to the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.98,0:14:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After making such an impact,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.48,0:14:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,everyone around the world will be very eager to purchase games made by the Schroeders!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.28,0:14:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In short, you're going to copy my company and do the exact same thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.16,0:14:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you are finally getting it, Kaiba.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.16,0:15:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If my synopsis proves accurate, the outcome of our Duel earlier will hardly matter at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.50,0:15:08.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as I can prove that I am a superior enterpriser to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.97,0:15:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell do you think a Duel is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.68,0:15:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the worst!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.68,0:15:15.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seto-{\i1}sama{\i0}, should we stop the Duel?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.72,0:15:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You cannot disqualify Leonhart like how you did I.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.73,0:15:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Duel has already gotten underway.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.02,0:15:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you stop it now, the KC Grand Prix will stumble at its climax...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.78,0:15:30.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the reputation of your company would be lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.24,0:15:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But doing that would also be to my benefit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.45,0:15:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is this going according to your plan, you damned simpleton?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.71,0:15:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi Mutou is the only person in this world who is qualified to be my rival!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.34,0:15:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way the likes of your little brother can beat him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.55,0:15:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if Yugi is not defeated, your plan would be meaningless.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.55,0:16:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because there's no Duelist in the world capable of defeating Yugi other than me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.10,0:16:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What terrifying confidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.90,0:16:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For real.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.02,0:16:05.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Kaiba for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.19,0:16:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This Duel will continue!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.07,0:16:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand here and watch as your planning and effort goes to waste!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.28,0:16:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi, I won't allow you to lose to any other Duelists.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.87,0:16:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kaiba.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.62,0:16:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leonhart!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.46,0:16:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a member of the Schroeder family and as my little brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.42,0:16:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must defeat Yugi Mutou!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.92,0:16:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do not dare to betray myself, nor your mother and father!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.80,0:16:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand, Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.30,0:16:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I come, Yugi-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.64,0:16:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Leon-{\i0}kun{\i1}...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.22,0:16:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I don't think he got close from the start in order to deceive us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.02,0:16:46.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I feel the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.48,0:16:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leon, are you really okay with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.90,0:16:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this kind of Duel really what you wish for?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.90,0:16:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you not a True Duelist?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.20,0:16:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do not listen to him, Leonhart!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.95,0:17:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, you need to do your best to defeat Yugi Mutou!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.12,0:17:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will be recognized as a member of the Schroeder family when you win!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.88,0:17:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think of how happy our mother would be!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.59,0:17:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do not forget this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.72,0:17:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.84,0:17:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leon...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.55,0:17:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi-{\i1}san{\i0}, I understand what you're trying to tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.72,0:17:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I became a Duelist because I admire you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.35,0:17:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But now I want to be of help to my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.15,0:17:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My brother needs me now... Me, who has no place in the Schroeder family.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.36,0:17:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why...  That's why I have to...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.24,0:17:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sieg... Siegfried! The home tutor is waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.95,0:17:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.41,0:17:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please teach me! Brother-
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.41,0:17:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That won't do, Leonhart.\N Siegfried has lessons now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.54,0:17:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.46,0:17:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come now, Siegfried.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.51,0:17:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sure you'll become a worthy successor and bring glory back to the family!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.01,0:18:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes, Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.22,0:18:04.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Leonhart, you mustn't interfere with Siegfried's studies.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.77,0:18:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You got that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.85,0:18:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes, Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.36,0:18:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, my brother was the star of hope for the Schroeder family.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.36,0:18:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And without disappointing anyone, he has also shown his talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.24,0:18:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm very proud of my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.58,0:18:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I couldn't help him in any way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.17,0:18:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, my encounter with Duel Monsters changed my life greatly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.46,0:18:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\an8}Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.00,0:18:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\an8}He really created them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.88,0:18:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't tear my eyes away from my favorite cards and Yugi-{\i1}san{\i0}'s Duels.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.64,0:18:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because the world that I'd imagined was becoming a reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.65,0:19:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The more I got exposed to Dueling, the more obsessed I became with that wonderful world.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.74,0:19:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.72,0:19:22.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The winner is, Leon Wilson-{\i0}kun{\i1}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.56,0:19:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.06,0:19:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Th-This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.94,0:19:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have been aware for quite some time that you
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.48,0:19:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}have been participating in such competitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.36,0:19:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And that you have hacked into their systems to make up fake names and experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.95,0:19:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have investigated everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.45,0:19:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I-I'm sorry! I really wanted to be a Duelist!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.50,0:19:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I knew Father and the rest wouldn't approve of this...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.09,0:19:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It isn't as if I'm angry about this or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.76,0:20:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}On the contrary, I am very proud to have such an outstanding brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.35,0:20:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Leonhart...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.60,0:20:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Although your computer skills and hacking skills are impressive...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.56,0:20:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Your Dueling skills are far more crucial to the Schroeder family.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.86,0:20:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm... crucial?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.32,0:20:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.15,0:20:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The time has come for you to use your skills for the greater good of the Schroeder family.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.99,0:20:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll do anything, Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.66,0:20:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In order to be of use to you, I'll do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.75,0:20:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So.. So for the sake of my brother, even if my opponent is you, Yugi-{\i1}san{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.55,0:20:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll defeat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.55,0:20:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leon...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.30,0:20:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But this doesn't seem right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.64,0:20:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Other Me, do we have no other choice but to fight him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.43,0:20:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Leon is serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.31,0:20:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.77,0:21:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Iron Hans in Attack Position!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.28,0:21:04.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And when this card is Summoned successfully,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.61,0:21:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can Special Summon Iron Knight from the deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.33,0:21:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.04,0:21:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the sake of my brother who needs me, I'll win this no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.83,0:21:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Special Summon Iron Knight!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.80,0:21:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is correct, Leonhart.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.52,0:21:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.14,0:21:59.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To show us now...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.44,0:22:08.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...a map isn't needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.91,0:22:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Only what tore apart the darkness...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.04,0:22:24.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...the hope that lies in my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.17,0:22:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Without deciding on a goal...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.60,0:22:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll just take a step toward my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.23,0:22:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}EYE'S, while I feel them...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.69,0:22:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll find your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.33,0:22:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh! EYE'S, if what I wished for...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.54,0:23:06.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...shudders my very soul...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.09,0:23:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...a Duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.50,0:23:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The climax of the KC Grand Prix has begun!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.34,0:23:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But to think that Leon-{\i1}kun{\i0} is actually Sieg's younger brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.59,0:23:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.80,0:23:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He enjoys his Duels so much...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.18,0:23:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But now he's treating Yugi as an enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.39,0:23:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leon-{\i1}kun{\i0}, are you really fine with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.10,0:23:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What we are more concerned about is the card he took from Sieg...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.39,0:23:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What card is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.44,0:23:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.81,0:23:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Golden Castle of Stromberg"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.86,0:23:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel standby!
